# Technical Stack

## Frontend

### Core Technologies
- **Next.js 15.2.1** - React framework for server-side rendering and static site generation
- **React 19.0.0** - JavaScript library for building user interfaces
- **TypeScript** - Typed JavaScript for better development experience
- **Tailwind CSS** - Utility-first CSS framework

### UI Components
- **Shadcn UI** - Component library built with Radix UI and Tailwind
- **Radix UI** - Low-level UI components (Dialogs, Avatars, Dropdown menus, etc.)
- **Embla Carousel** - Carousel/slider component
- **Lucide React** - Icon library

### State Management & Data Fetching
- **React Query (TanStack Query)** - Data fetching and caching
- **SWR** - Data fetching with stale-while-revalidate strategy
- **React Hook Form** - Form management
- **Zod** - Schema validation

## Infrastructure

- **Nx** - Build system and monorepo tooling

## Backend


### Database
- **PostgreSQL** - Relational database (via Neon Database serverless)
- **Drizzle ORM** - TypeScript ORM for database interaction

### Authentication
- **Privy** - Web3 authentication
- **Web3Auth** - Blockchain authentication
- **jose** - JWT handling

## Blockchain Integration
- **Ethereum** - Smart contract platform
- **Wagmi** - React hooks for Ethereum
- **Viem** - TypeScript interface for Ethereum
- **Hardhat** - Development environment for Ethereum
- **OpenZeppelin Contracts** - Smart contract library

## Testing & Development
- **Vitest** - Testing framework for Vite
- **Jest** - JavaScript testing framework
- **Playwright** - End-to-end testing
- **Storybook** - UI component explorer
- **ESLint** - Code linting
- **Prettier** - Code formatting

## Internationalization
- **i18n** - Custom internationalization package

## Deployment
- **Vercel** - Deployment platform

## Build Tools
- **Vite** - Build tool and development server
- **Rollup** - JavaScript module bundler
- **SWC** - JavaScript/TypeScript compiler